ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectMedicine Hat & District Chamber of Commerce (Alberta) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the MEDICINE HAT & DISTRICT CHAMBER OF COMMERCE, in Alberta, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Town of Medicine Hat and the Electoral District of Medicine Hat to the City of Medicine Hat, the Town of Redcliff and the Municipal District of Cypress County, which includes Wild Horse, Seven Persons, Elkwater, Irvine, Walsh, Dunmore, Schuler, Hilda, Suffield, Ralston, Veinerville and Desert Blume.
